question: What are the ids of stations that are located in San Francisco and have average bike availability above 10.

question: Which film is rented at a fee of 0.99 and has less than 3 in the inventory? List the film title and id.

FILTER(?T1_rental_rate = 0.99) . FILTER (?T1_title in (?T2_title)) . FILTER (?T1_film_id in (?T2_film_id)) .   ?T2 a :film . ?T3 a :inventory . ?T3 :inventory\#ref-film_id ?T2 .  ?T2 :film\#title ?T2_title . ?T2 :film\#film_id ?T2_film_id .     GROUP BY ?T2_title ?T2_film_id   HAVING(count( *)  < 3)      }

FILTER (?T1_asset_id in (?T3_asset_id)) . FILTER (?T1_asset_details in (?T3_asset_details)) .   ?T3 a :assets . ?T4 a :fault_log . ?T4 :fault_log\#ref-asset_id ?T3 .  ?T3 :assets\#asset_id ?T3_asset_id . ?T3 :assets\#asset_details ?T3_asset_details .     GROUP BY ?T3_asset_id ?T3_asset_details   HAVING(count( *)  < 2)      } GROUP BY ?T1_asset_id ?T1_asset_details   HAVING(count( *)  = 2)

question: How many assets does each maintenance contract contain? List the number and the contract id.

question: Which third party companies have at least 2 maintenance engineers or have at least 2 maintenance contracts? List the company id and name.
query: SELECT distinct?col1?col2 WHERE { { SELECT (?T1_company_id as ?col1) (?T1_company_name as ?col2) WHERE { ?T1 a :third_party_companies . ?T13 a :maintenance_contracts . ?T13 :maintenance_contracts\#ref-maintenance_contract_company_id ?T1 .  ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_id ?T1_company_id . ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_name ?T1_company_name . ?T14 a :assets . ?T14 :assets\#ref-maintenance_contract_id ?T13 .  ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_id ?T1_company_id . ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_name ?T1_company_name . ?T15 a :fault_log . ?T15 :fault_log\#ref-asset_id ?T14 .  ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_id ?T1_company_id . ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_name ?T1_company_name . ?T16 a :engineer_visits . ?T16 :engineer_visits\#ref-fault_log_entry_id ?T15 .  ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_id ?T1_company_id . ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_name ?T1_company_name . ?T2 a :maintenance_engineers . ?T16 :engineer_visits\#ref-engineer_id ?T2 .  ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_id ?T1_company_id . ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_name ?T1_company_name .   }} UNION {SELECT (?T1_company_id as ?col1) (?T1_company_name as ?col2) WHERE { ?T1 a :third_party_companies . ?T2 a :maintenance_contracts . ?T2 :maintenance_contracts\#ref-maintenance_contract_company_id ?T1 .  ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_id ?T1_company_id . ?T1 :third_party_companies\#company_name ?T1_company_name .        } GROUP BY ?T1_company_id ?T1_company_name   HAVING(count( *)  >= 2)  } } GROUP BY ?T1_company_id ?T1_company_name   HAVING(count( *)  >= 2)

question: What is the name and id of the staff who recorded the fault log but has not contacted any visiting engineers?
query: SELECT distinct?col1?col2 WHERE { { SELECT (?T1_staff_name as ?col1) (?T1_staff_id as ?col2) WHERE { ?T1 a :staff . ?T1 :staff\#staff_name ?T1_staff_name . ?T1 :staff\#staff_id ?T1_staff_id .   }}  MINUS {SELECT (?T2_staff_name as ?col1) (?T2_staff_id as ?col2) WHERE { ?T2 a :staff . ?T2 :staff\#staff_name ?T2_staff_name . ?T2 :staff\#staff_id ?T2_staff_id .        }     } }
